
---

# 🧹 **.gitignore (copy–paste this into .gitignore)**

```gitignore
# Ignore Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Ignore Jupyter notebook checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Ignore virtual environments
venv/
env/

# Ignore data files that shouldn't be public
data/*.csv
data/*.xlsx
data/*.json

# Ignore system files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
